7
00:00:43,091 --> 00:00:45,621
<i>I'm not that strongly-built.</i>

8
00:00:45,831 --> 00:00:52,631
<i>Here I go, at my dauntless pace.</i>

9
00:00:53,841 --> 00:00:58,831
<i>Pass away, today's
sadness, raining in the sun!</i>

10
00:00:59,081 --> 00:01:04,101
<i>Hesitation, repetition,
dreaming all night, all night.</i>

11
00:01:04,521 --> 00:01:09,481
<i>Farewell sadness,
to outer space you go!</i>

12
00:01:09,821 --> 00:01:14,761
<i>Look to the sky and shout
at the top of your lungs!</i>

13
00:01:16,261 --> 00:01:18,521
<i>At this tempo!</i>

14
00:01:25,841 --> 00:01:28,171
<i>Right now, at this tempo!</i>

15
00:01:28,171 --> 00:01:29,871
<i>Genshiken
Right now, at this tempo!</i>

16
00:01:53,201 --> 00:01:55,531
