is why she came along with us...

20
00:02:06,611 --> 00:02:07,801
Better late than never.

21
00:02:07,951 --> 00:02:08,971
I'm sorry...

22
00:02:09,081 --> 00:02:10,641
Hey, isn't Kohsaka here yet?

23
00:02:10,951 --> 00:02:13,251
Didn't he just message us
that he's in the parking lot?

24
00:02:13,881 --> 00:02:15,481
So slow...

25
00:02:15,991 --> 00:02:17,891
Today's the day I make my move!

26
00:02:19,321 --> 00:02:21,811
I have a feeling it's
a waste of effort...

27
00:02:22,631 --> 00:02:23,751
C'mon, let's go.

28
00:02:26,631 --> 00:02:32,191
<i>Episode 10, The Fetishism of Leisure
Spending Taking into Account Economic Effect</i>

29
