I won't be humiliated by a tan.

69
00:04:56,211 --> 00:04:57,701
Well, there you have it.

70
00:04:57,851 --> 00:04:59,011
Is that true?

71
00:04:59,121 --> 00:04:59,181
Come on, let's go.

72
00:04:59,181 --> 00:05:00,771
<i>Yes, it is.
Come on, let's go.</i>

73
00:05:12,131 --> 00:05:13,861
Oh, that was nothing.

74
00:05:17,901 --> 00:05:19,701
M-Monkey...

