This is a time-honored
Japanese tradition!

104
00:07:02,441 --> 00:07:03,841
Yes, I know that!

105
00:07:03,941 --> 00:07:05,241
I will not yield!

106
00:07:05,511 --> 00:07:07,311
Have it your way.

107
00:07:07,881 --> 00:07:09,851
Then it's the "m" in "charm."

108
00:07:10,111 --> 00:07:13,171
M-M-M-Mass
production model...

109
00:07:13,281 --> 00:07:16,081
