127
00:08:18,921 --> 00:08:20,351
O-Ohno?

128
00:08:21,181 --> 00:08:22,381
Was that intentional?

129
00:08:22,491 --> 00:08:24,451
She sure is a clever one...

130
00:08:25,591 --> 00:08:27,611
Aw, I got my bottom wet...

131
00:08:29,961 --> 00:08:31,551
A-Are you okay?

132
00:08:31,701 --> 00:08:32,531
Yes...

133
00:08:32,661 --> 00:08:35,131
Let's play in the sand some.

134
00:08:35,271 --> 00:08:36,101
Good idea.

135
00:08:36,431 --> 00:08:38,031
I can handle that...

136
00:08:38,501 --> 00:08:41,871
I can see why Kasukabe
didn't want to be around us...

137
00:08:42,041 --> 00:08:43,271
Yeah, really.

138
00:08:43,371 --> 00:08:45,971
Kohsaka, how about lunch?

139
00:08:46,281 --> 00:08:48,511
Hmm, what do you suppose we should
eat?

140
00:08:50,281 --> 00:08:52,251
Look at that, you finally came out.

141
00:08:52,421 --> 00:08:54,541
Well, it was inevitable.

142
00:08:55,351 --> 00:08:56,651
After coming all this way...

143
00:08:57,521 --> 00:08:59,451
It would've been a waste not to.

144
00:09:00,621 --> 00:09:03,991
Weren't we supposed to stay
a 10m radius away from you?

145
00:09:04,161 --> 00:09:05,021
Eh?

146
00:09:05,401 --> 00:09:07,331
Oh, that was just a joke.

147
00:09:08,971 --> 00:09:12,031
Kohsaka, would you like
to go get a cold drink?

148
00:09:12,201 --> 00:09:13,171
That sounds good.

149
00:09:13,671 --> 00:09:15,541
It's not a joke in your case.

150
00:09:19,011 --> 00:09:21,571
Darn, maybe this is useless.

151
00:09:26,181 --> 00:09:27,651
Huh? What gives?

152
00:09:28,391 --> 00:09:29,681
Why are you here?

153
00:09:30,251 --> 00:09:31,811
S-Same to you.

154
00:09:32,761 --> 00:09:35,951
So that's how it is, huh?

155
00:09:36,631 --> 00:09:39,031
No, that ain't how it is!

156
00:09:39,661 --> 00:09:41,391
What's that supposed to mean?

157
00:09:41,531 --> 00:09:43,291
It's none of your business.

158
00:09:43,571 --> 00:09:45,691
You think you can talk to me that way?

159
00:09:45,771 --> 00:09:47,241
I told you, you're wrong!

160
00:09:48,411 --> 00:09:49,371
What the hell's with you?

161
00:09:53,211 --> 00:09:55,731
Shouting annoys those around you.

162
00:09:59,321 --> 00:10:03,121
Look buddy, we're friends
of this girl's brother!

163
00:10:03,621 --> 00:10:05,281
He's here with us too.

164
00:10:05,661 --> 00:10:06,621
Over there!

165
00:10:15,031 --> 00:10:15,691
H-Hi...

166
00:10:15,801 --> 00:10:16,731
Yeah, hi...

167
00:10:19,601 --> 00:10:23,331
You didn't come here
alone either, right?

168
00:10:23,611 --> 00:10:25,601
Let's not start any trouble in public.

169
00:10:28,281 --> 00:10:29,641
I'll message you later.

170
00:10:29,751 --> 00:10:31,241
Don't bother.

171
00:10:36,451 --> 00:10:38,441
Damn, I am so fallin' for him.

172
00:10:39,061 --> 00:10:39,781
You can move now!

173
00:10:40,291 --> 00:10:43,051
Are you too stupid to
stay out of trouble?

174
00:10:43,331 --> 00:10:45,261
That guy thinks he's a
bigshot for yelling at people!

175
00:10:46,061 --> 00:10:47,221
Sorry, sorry...

176
00:10:49,031 --> 00:10:51,091
You sure were quick to run.

177
00:10:51,201 --> 00:10:53,291
Because I'm an unreliable bodyguard.

178
00:10:55,511 --> 00:10:56,701
Are you okay?

179
00:10:56,811 --> 00:10:57,531
Yeah...

180
00:11:04,781 --> 00:11:06,651
I'm no match for her...

181
00:11:14,561 --> 00:11:16,351
Don't destroy it, Saki.

182
00:11:16,491 --> 00:11:17,621
Ah, yeah...

183
00:11:18,131 --> 00:11:20,821
I would've already done it
back in grade school...

184
00:11:21,131 --> 00:11:23,221
That's a closed club, there...

185
00:11:23,331 --> 00:11:24,431
Sure is.

186
00:11:24,571 --> 00:11:26,261
That's Cagliostro Castle.

187
00:11:26,371 --> 00:11:29,071
It's true. They've even
built in the clock tower.

188
00:11:29,371 --> 00:11:31,671
