and the Chimneysweep?

189
00:11:31,811 --> 00:11:33,241
There you go again.

190
00:11:33,381 --> 00:11:36,211
I'm an "originals only"
kind of guy at heart.

191
00:11:36,351 --> 00:11:38,441
But you like Clarisse.

192
00:11:38,521 --> 00:11:39,571
That's different!

193
00:11:39,681 --> 00:11:41,651
I also like The Fuma Conspiracy.

194
00:11:43,291 --> 00:11:44,811
You recognize the Furukawa Lupin?

195
00:11:45,091 --> 00:11:46,561
It's a good movie, though.

196
00:11:47,221 --> 00:11:51,351
For curveballs I'd love to give
the illusory Oshii version as an...

197
00:11:51,461 --> 00:11:53,551
