Legend of the Gold of Babylon...

201
00:12:01,571 --> 00:12:03,131
Wish we could have seen that.

202
00:12:03,241 --> 00:12:06,301
Well, no use figuring the
age of a dead child.

203
00:12:06,381 --> 00:12:07,431
That's true.

204
00:12:09,181 --> 00:12:10,311
I've got it!

205
00:12:10,411 --> 00:12:12,571
A way to fight off Kasukabe...

206
00:12:20,391 --> 00:12:22,121
Why'd you come to my place?

207
00:12:22,231 --> 00:12:24,131
Who cares, just let me stay a while.

208
00:12:24,361 --> 00:12:25,331
Huh?

209
00:12:26,161 --> 00:12:28,601
