an advantage, genetics.

212
00:12:35,341 --> 00:12:37,431
So show me some videos, some anime.

213
00:12:37,671 --> 00:12:40,541
But don't you hate them?

214
00:12:40,611 --> 00:12:41,771
Just do it.

215
00:12:41,911 --> 00:12:46,371
