I want hardcore otaku shows.

216
00:13:05,441 --> 00:13:06,331
No!

217
00:13:06,441 --> 00:13:08,371
If even one of us leaves
we'll be eliminated.

218
00:13:08,441 --> 00:13:09,741
I can't go on.

219
00:13:10,241 --> 00:13:13,471
I'm sorry I'm gutless,
but this is my limit.

220
00:13:14,641 --> 00:13:15,271
Tokino!

221
00:13:15,381 --> 00:13:17,541
Outside, outside, outside, outside.

222
00:13:17,611 --> 00:13:19,451
Just hold out a little longer!

223
